  "name": "SettleMint DALP for Italy — Consob-Aligned Digital Asset Platform",
  "htmlTitle": "SettleMint DALP for Italy: Consob-Aligned Digital Asset and Tokenized Securities Platform",
  "metaDescription": "DALP for Italy: Consob-aligned compliance, EU DLT Pilot Regime asset templates, MiCA-ready stablecoins, and Italian data residency for tokenized assets.",
  "linkRelCanonicalUrl": "https://www.settlemint.com/for/italy",
  "templatePath": "Marketplace/One_Elements child-theme/templates/One - Competitors Comparison.html",
  "headHtml": "<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\n  \"mainEntity\": [\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"What is DALP for Italy?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"DALP is SettleMint's Digital Asset Lifecycle Platform for regulated financial institutions. For Italy, it provides Consob-aligned compliance controls, EU DLT Pilot Regime-compatible asset templates, MiCA-ready stablecoin infrastructure, and Italian data residency for tokenized asset operations.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"Does DALP support the EU DLT Pilot Regime for Italian institutions?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"DALP provides infrastructure compatible with the EU DLT Pilot Regime: bond and equity templates with full lifecycle logic for tokenized securities issuance, transfer, and servicing under the Consob-supervised DLT framework.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"How does DALP support Consob and MiCA compliance requirements?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"DALP enforces compliance ex-ante: 12 on-chain compliance module types cover Consob investor eligibility, transfer restrictions, country-based controls, and MiCA ART/EMT issuer requirements. Every transfer is validated before execution, not reviewed after.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"Can DALP be deployed within Italian/EU data borders?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"Yes. DALP supports on-premises, Italian-hosted cloud, and hybrid deployment via Kubernetes and Helm. All data stays within Italy/EU for GDPR and Consob data sovereignty requirements.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n</script>\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"SoftwareApplication\",\n  \"name\": \"SettleMint DALP\",\n  \"description\": \"Digital Asset Lifecycle Platform for Italian financial institutions and fintechs. Covers issuance, compliance, servicing, settlement, and custody under Consob oversight and MiCA via a single EVM-based platform.\",\n  \"applicationCategory\": \"FinanceApplication\",\n  \"operatingSystem\": \"Cloud, On-Premises, Kubernetes\",\n  \"offers\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Offer\",\n    \"price\": \"0\",\n    \"priceCurrency\": \"USD\"\n  },\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"SettleMint\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.settlemint.com\"\n  }\n}\n</script>",
