                  "label": "Rich Text",
                  "name": "widget_tokeny_table_richtext",
                  "params": {
                    "css_class": "dnd-module",
                    "html": "<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; color:#1a1a2e;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"><col style=\"width:50%\"></colgroup>\n<thead style=\"background-color:#000048 !important; color:#ffffff !important;\">\n<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5;\">\n<th style=\"padding:12px 16px; text-align:left; color:#ffffff !important; background-color:#000048 !important; border:1px solid #1a1a5e;\">What Italian institutions need</th>\n<th style=\"padding:12px 16px; text-align:left; color:#ffffff !important; background-color:#000048 !important; border:1px solid #1a1a5e;\">How DALP delivers it</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">Consob compliance for digital asset issuance and investor eligibility</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">12 on-chain compliance module types enforce Consob-aligned transfer restrictions, investor eligibility, and jurisdictional controls enforced ex-ante on every transaction</td>\n</tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">MiCA compliance for stablecoin and token issuers</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">Stablecoin template with supply limits, reserve-ratio enforcement, and MiCA-aligned compliance modules covering ART and EMT issuer requirements</td>\n</tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">EU DLT Pilot Regime participation for tokenized securities</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">Bond and equity templates with full lifecycle logic for issuance, distribution, and servicing under the EU DLT Pilot Regime framework</td>\n</tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">Atomic DvP settlement aligned with Borsa Italiana and Monte Titoli infrastructure</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">Atomic DvP/XvP settlement with HTLC hashlock; REST and ISO 20022 API connectivity for integration with Italian settlement infrastructure</td>\n</tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">DORA operational resilience for Banca d'Italia and Consob-regulated platforms</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">21 pre-built Grafana dashboards, three-pillar observability (VictoriaMetrics, Loki, Tempo), and durable workflows that survive infrastructure failures for DORA compliance</td>\n</tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">Italian and EU data residency, GDPR compliance</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">On-prem, Italian-cloud, and hybrid deployment via Kubernetes and Helm; all data stays within defined EU perimeters for GDPR compliance</td>\n</tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">Integration with Italian banking and core financial systems</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; background:#f8f8fc; color: #1a1a2e;\">REST, GraphQL, and webhook APIs; ISO 20022 connectivity for SEPA and Italian banking system integration with institutions such as Intesa Sanpaolo and UniCredit</td>\n</tr><tr style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #d9d9e3;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">Maker-checker governance for regulated issuers</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 16px; border:1px solid #d9d9e3; color: #1a1a2e;\">Dual-approval workflows with RBAC/ABAC access controls for issuance, transfer approval, and corporate action processing under Consob oversight</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
                    "module_id": 1155639,
                    "schema_version": 2
