                        "cta_link": {"no_follow": false, "open_in_new_tab": false, "url": {"href": ""}},
                        "cta_text": "",
                        "description": "<p>12 on-chain compliance module types enforce Consob investor eligibility, transfer restrictions, and jurisdictional controls. Bond and equity templates support tokenized securities issuance under the EU DLT Pilot Regime with full lifecycle logic from issuance to redemption.</p>",
                        "number_text": "Consob and DLT Pilot-aligned compliance"
                      },
                      {
                        "cta_link": {"no_follow": false, "open_in_new_tab": false, "url": {"href": ""}},
                        "cta_text": "",
                        "description": "<p>Italy is a key MiCA jurisdiction. DALP ships a stablecoin template with supply limits, reserve-ratio controls, and 12 compliance module types covering ART and EMT issuer requirements under MiCA, enforced ex-ante on every transaction before execution.</p>",
                        "number_text": "MiCA-ready from day one"
                      },
                      {
                        "cta_link": {"no_follow": false, "open_in_new_tab": false, "url": {"href": ""}},
                        "cta_text": "",
                        "description": "<p>Deploy on-premises or in Italian-hosted cloud via Kubernetes and Helm. Data stays within Italy/EU. 21 Grafana dashboards and three-pillar observability directly support DORA operational resilience requirements for Consob and Banca d'Italia-regulated platforms.</p>",
                        "number_text": "Italian data residency and DORA resilience"
